## Common Hardware Configurations

### JetBot Configuration
```yaml
# JetBot with stereo cameras and IMU
- Jetson Xavier NX (8GB RAM)
- 16GB eMMC storage
- Dual 1280x720 cameras (MIPI CSI-2)
- MPU-9250 IMU via I2C
- TB6612FNG motor driver via GPIO
- 2x 6V DC motors with encoders
- 11.1V LiPo battery with BMS
- Active cooling fan
```

### Sensor Wiring Guide
- I2C: Connect SDA to Pin 3, SCL to Pin 5 (GPIO I2C bus)
- SPI: Connect MOSI, MISO, SCLK, and CS pins appropriately
- UART: Connect TX to Pin 8, RX to Pin 10 (Serial1)
- GPIO: Use pins 7, 11, 12, 13, 15, 16, 18, 22, 29, 31, 32, 33, 35, 36, 37, 38, 40

